        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n@Michal: Good comments, like also Milan commented that instead of template we should use lineinfile module not to destroy existing entries.\nJust that none of the comments relate to this commit, but the original code itself:)\nI can improve those however as part of this molecule commit or in separate commit?",
